BRC15
[normal]Submission from Robert [bold]Hansler[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]This submission is my personal point of view regarding the current state of the electrical trade and the registration schemes such as those operated by ECA/NICEIC, NASPIT and others. 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Written evidence by Robert 
[normal]Hansler
[normal]. I am a Joint Industry Board (J.I.B.) Approved Electrician (Registration number 31809) with forty years in the trade.  
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]The past 20 years being shared between inspection and testing electrical installations, part-time te
[normal]aching of electrical work and working in field of electrical and general Health and Safety  
[normal]&#xa0;
